      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h1"
    },
    {
      "_key": "aac87e52bb77",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "e23db8a92066",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "Now, you’ve got to understand that I was born in the ’50s, grew up in the ’60s, and played in a rock band five nights a week throughout the ’70s. Guys like Rick Wakeman (Yes) and Keith Emerson (ELP) were my influences, as were bands like Gentle Giant and Genesis. I’ve been searching for VST instruments that emulate keyboards like the Mellotron, Rhodes, B3, Clav, Minimoog, etc., that I used to own and play (I still have my B3 and Minimoog)."
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "658e60c7d447",
      "_type": "image",
      "alt": "Logic Pro VSTs",
      "asset": {
        "_ref": "image-c28b765d55c5ec3594847fa0317c6ecbc039ed15-1800x1200-png",
        "_type": "reference"
      }
    },
    {
      "_key": "294e26f7382d",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "80cab0e2df85",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "For a while, I got into Virtual Instruments (VSTi) to record with, and it was nice to have all the keyboards I once owned or could never have owned available at my fingertips to compose with. I still have vintage keys, like my Hammond B3, Minimoog, Polymoog, EMU Proteus/1, ESQ-1, Yamaha TX7s, and Roland MKB-300 MIDI Controller. There’s something about having the hardware that virtual instruments can’t replace."
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "be39f9fdc589",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "5016d39bd118",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "If you’re working with MIDI, high-quality virtual instruments and audio plug-ins are essential. I use "
        },
        {
          "_key": "bdfdaadc4fb9",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "0b43e54c4fc8"
          ],
          "text": "Waves"
        },
        {
          "_key": "b222a5b15062",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": " plug-ins, and you can get a 10% coupon if you purchase through this "
        },
